name: Italian Dungeons - At The Small Door
description: Using real photos of Città di Fermo in the Marche region in Italy, this artwork aims to mix the atmosphere of the historical center of this city with RPG games and dungeons aesthetics. This piece is an allegory about the experience of being a foreigner living in the historic atmosphere of ancient Italian medieval cities. - Artist: Luiz André Gama - www.luizandregama.com  Date of Creation: 2016 - Size: 4827x7087px.
